This toolset is written for to accommodate Visual Vertex's Muster (render farm manager)
Built for use with Maya without Qt packages. Could be extended for other 3D applications

author = Jesse Denton
created = 07/02/2013
version = 1.0.1


useage:

from musterSubmit import musterUI
musterUI.open()



module description:
-----------------------------------------------------------------------
MUSTERTOOLS.py:

MusterDatabase()
Used to connect to the sqlite database to aquire basic table data.
MusterTools()
used to connect to the muster executable to send and recieve calls.

-----------------------------------------------------------------------
MUSTERUI.py

MusterSubmit()
Main window class for use with Autodesk Maya.
MusterSubmit_Tabs()
tabs class link to main window for layer creation and settings

-----------------------------------------------------------------------
PROJECTTOOLS.py

PRAFileInfo()
basic file info api. gathers information from a given file path or name.


-----------------------------------------------------------------------
